title: Cal Smart Supercharged Salmon Salad with Creamy Dressing
description: This salad is just what you need on a beautiful summer evening. It's elegant, simple and oh so tasty. We're giving you all the best toppings: crisp cucumbers, crunchy pepitas and a gorgeous piece of pan-seared salmon.

